snippet.textDisplay:
Understanding that this is reality TV, the fact remains that it is astonishing how many people are in business that have no clue about what they are doing, no real aptitude, but muddle about even when they have all of the proper implements needed to do the job very well or get the people they need to do them, from staff to accountants...amazing.

Then, there are the ones either too stupid, inept or disinterested (in their own business) even after they are instructed on how to proceed. I also wonder if they are motivated to fail for whatever reason, including cover for some kind of a scam.
